'''Cumar Bin Khadaab R.C'''(Carabi 586-590 عمر بن لخطاب ) waxaa kaloo loo yaqiin [[Cumar Alfaruuq]] waana Amiirka labaad ee [[Amiirul Mu'miniin]]ka, waana [[Khaliif|khaliifkii]] ugu horeeyay ee loogu waco, wuxuuna ka tirsan yahay [[Afarta Khulafo al'Raashidiin]] waana saxaabi katirsan asxaabta [[Nabi Muxamed S.C.W]] [[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]].
Waxa uu kamid ahaa tobankii Saxaabi ee loogu bishaareeyay [[Jano|janada]] iyaga oo [[duni|ifka]] jooga. Waxa uu ahaa ruuxii ugu horeeyay ee sameeya [[kalandar|kalandarka Taariikhda Islaamka]] ee [[Hijri]]ga.<ref>"[[kalandar|kalandarka Taariikhda Islaamka]] ee [[Hijri]]ga"</ref> Xiligiisii maamulka dowlada Islaamku waxa uu gaaray [[Libya|Liibiya]], [[Falastiin]], [[Masar]] iyo [[Siiriya|Shaam]] (maanta loo yaqaano [[Suuriya]]).<ref>"[[Libya|Liibiya]], [[Falastiin]], [[Masar]] iyo [[Siiriya|Shaam]] (maanta loo yaqaano [[Suuriya]])"</ref>
